  Learn more about how ChatGPT can be used to support various educational tasks.

- [OpenAI's User Guide](https://openai.com/guides)  
  Access official documentation and best practices from OpenAI.

---

By following these steps, you’ll be able to leverage ChatGPT to enhance your classroom, streamline your planning, and better meet the needs of your students. 

And yes, this guide was written by ChatGPT itself, which is a great example of how AI can be used to create helpful resources!
